    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You could use the <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/lang/String.html#charAt(int)\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><code>String.charAt(int index)</code></a> method result as the parameter for <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/lang/String.html#valueOf(char)\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">String.valueOf(char c)</a>. </p>\n\n<pre><code>String.valueOf(myString.charAt(3)) // This will return a string of the character on the 3rd position.\n</code></pre>\n"
